{"tid":116253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"解構秒回秘技！fb紅人「文生」真身現《蘋果》…原來幾靚仔！","createTime":"2017-02-11T08:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T21:30:59.000Z","uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":109,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"a17dfc5d687312249d177e813a78a5a8bd62fba4","tid":116253,"uid":25038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:46:36.000Z","msg":"近嚟老是常出現、差唔多每個《蘋果》fb、《100毛》、「名校Secret」等等嘅各大小媒體FB都會見到佢嘅留言 &mdash;&mdash; 一個名叫Leoman嘅黑人「文生」。頭像係一個黑人男子，大家可能會幻想佢係一個「又毒又宅」嘅廢青。<br />\n<br />\n估唔到自稱24、25歲嘅文生，真人都幾潮，仲一啲都唔黑添！有留意開文生fb，都知佢有兩個嗜好，就係瘋狂留言同埋種栗米。問到佢點解咁多嘢唔種要種粟米？文生話：「因為我哋嗰邊(剛果)都係食粟米多。」好鬼入戲。<br />\n<br />\n文生個專頁成立短短兩個星期，就勁吸到9,000幾個like，佢就好多謝網民嘅支持，仲話一開始都冇諗過會爆紅：「其實都係隨心所欲，見到咩想留就留(言)，冇諗過話要點樣。」<br />\n<br />\n至於會唔會以瓊姐(King Jer娛樂台)為目標，文生話：「我都有留意過佢嘅，都有少少興趣想識佢嘅。」想了解文生更多，見證佢嘅「秒回秘技」有幾快？即刻去片啦！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170211&amp;guid=56288316&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170211%26guid%3D56288316%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&d=3iEKCEnQ8TgOeM43nfYZ1ywN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=5085974a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170211%26guid%3D56288316%26category_guid%3D7018882%26category%3Dinstant&h=c68d71d3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170211&amp;guid=56288316&amp;category_guid=7018882&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"8f7c00502ccf54c277367416028ea2bdf6c9ad76","tid":116253,"uid":3095,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:48:03.000Z","msg":"on鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34153031064708cb13fe2d3f7c3cb95036eff0e4","tid":116253,"uid":10089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T08:48:30.000Z","msg":"毒果真係好撚低質"},{"pid":"7db713aa1db7bc85235a9f809c798b5cb1e3de0c","tid":11625